title: Replacement Power Supply/AC Adapter for Korg Electribe Products: EA-1, ER-1, EM-1, ES-1 and all MKII/MK2 versions of those models (Aftermarket)91
features: Slim Design Frees up Space on Power Strip by Occupying One Outlet
Safety standard compliant: FCC, CE, RoHS. Safety Features: High Efficiency and Reliability, Automatic Overload cut-off, Automatic Thermal cut-off, Short circuit and Over Voltage protection
description: The Silverline Audio 9-volt power supply will keep the music going all night long. The slim design helps to reserve valuable real estate on your power strip or wall outlet by occupying only one space.

Silverline Audio's aftermarket power supplies have been carefully analyzed for compatibility. They have a center negative pin that is required by these products. Do not use positive center pin power supplies with these units! It will damage them.
This Silverline Audio aftermarket replacement AC Power Adapter is designed to be compatible with the following Korg Electribe products: EA-1 ER-1 ES-1 EM-1 EA-1 MKII ER-1 MKII ES-1 MKII

Features: Slim Design Frees up Space on Power Strip by Occupying One Outlet Input Volt Range: 100-240V (Worldwide Compliant) Safety standard compliant: FCC, CE, RoHS Safety Features: High Efficiency and Reliability, Automatic Overload cut-off, Automatic Thermal cut-off, Short circuit and Over Voltage protection
